me}}] A new subscriber has (been) registered!','yes'),(22752,'wppb_admin_emailc_default_registration_email_content','\r\n<p>New subscriber on {{site_name}}.</p>\r\n<p>Username:{{username}}</p>\r\n<p>E-mail:{{user_email}}</p>\r\n','yes'),(22753,'wppb_admin_emailc_registration_with_admin_approval_email_subject','[{{site_name}}] A new subscriber has (been) registered!','yes'),(22754,'wppb_admin_emailc_registration_with_admin_approval_email_content','\r\n<p>New subscriber on {{site_name}}.</p>\r\n<p>Username:{{username}}</p>\r\n<p>E-mail:{{user_email}}</p>\r\n<p>The Admin Approval feature was activated at the time of registration,\r\nso please remember that you need to approve this user before he/she can log in!</p>\r\n','yes'),(22755,'wppb_user_emailc_default_registration_email_subject','[{{site_name}}] Enjoy Your New Account','yes'),(22756,'wppb_user_emailc_default_registration_email_content','<p>\r\n  Hi {{first_name}} {{last_name}},<br />\r\n  Thank you for verifying your account. You’re one of us now!\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  Want to upload your first article? Don’t hesitate and click the link below:<br />\r\n  <a href=\"http://magazine.backfeed.cc/submit-article\">Submit New Article</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Not in the mood right now?  Why don’t have a look at what others have written and help evaluating their work? You’ll get a dividend of their token bounty if you helped to reach community consensus.<br /> \r\n<a href=\"http://magazine.backfeed.cc/submit-article\">The Raw Space</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Or just enjoy our community curated and verified stories on the <a href=\"http://magazine.backfeed.cc/\">{{site_name}} Front Page</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	See you around!<br />\r\n	The Backfeed Community.\r\n</p>','yes'),(22757,'wppb_user_emailc_registr_w_email_confirm_email_subject','[{{site_name}}] Confirm Your New Account','yes'),(22758,'wppb_user_emailc_registr_w_email_confirm_email_content','<p>\r\n  Welcome {{first_name}} {{last_name}},<br />\r\n  Thank you for joining the {{site_name}}.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nPlease click the link below to verify your account and start mining content!<br />\r\n{{{activation_link}}}\r\n</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://magazine.backfeed.cc/faq\">FAQ</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n  See you in a minute!<br />\r\n  The Backfeed Community.\r\n</p>','yes'),(22759,'wppb_user_emailc_registration_with_admin_approval_email_subject','A new account has been created for you on {{site_name}}','yes'),(22760,'wppb_user_emailc_registration_with_admin_approval_email_content','<h3>Welcome to {{site_name}}!</h3>\r\n<p>Your username is:{{username}} and password:{{password}}</p>\r\n<p>Before you can access your account, an administrator needs to approve it. You will be notified via email.</p>\r\n','yes'),(22761,'wppb_user_emailc_admin_approval_notif_approved_email_subject','Your account on {{site_name}} has been approved!','yes'),(22762,'wppb_user_emailc_admin_approval_notif_approved_email_content','<h3>Good News!</h3>\r\n<p>An administrator has just approved your account: {{username}} on {{site_name}}.</p>\r\n','yes'),(22763,'wppb_user_emailc_admin_approval_notif_unapproved_email_subject','Your account on {{site_name}} has been unapproved!','yes'),(22764,'wppb_user_emailc_admin_approval_notif_unapproved_email_content','<h3>Hello,</h3>\r\n<p>Unfortunatelly an administrator has just unapproved your account: {{username}} on {{site_name}}.</p>\r\n','yes'),(22766,'wppb_admin_emailc_common_settings_header','These settings are also replicated in the \"User Email Customizer\" settings-page upon save. Valid tags {{reply_to}} and {{site_name}}','yes'),(22767,'wppb_admin_emailc_user_password_reset_email_subject','[{{site_name}}] Password Successfully Reset for {{username}}','yes'),(22768,'wppb_admin_emailc_user_password_reset_email_content','\r\n<p>{{username}} has requested a password change via the password reset feature.</p>\r\n<p>His/her new password is: {{password}}</p>\r\n','yes'),(22769,'wppb_user_emailc_reset_email_subject','[{{site_name}}] P