hers and building startups together.</p>','Stigmergic Economy And Large-Scale, Decentralized Networks - Matan Field','','inherit','closed','closed','','186-revision-v1','','','2016-03-21 08:26:27','2016-03-21 08:26:27','',186,'http://magazine.backfeed.cc/186-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(551,1,'2016-03-21 08:27:56','2016-03-21 08:27:56','<p><span style=\"line-height: 28.8px;\">[embed]</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.8px;\">https://youtu.be/LPE7Z9Fu5Nc</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.8px;\">[/embed]</span><br />What would it look like if billions of people would be spontaneously, freely and systematically cooperating with each other, on anything? Imagine a self-organized world, with Facebook network but no Facebook Inc., a decentralized transportation network without Lyft or Uber, peer-to-peer marketplaces replacing eBay or Amazon, millions of people insuring each others and building startups together.</p>','Stigmergic Economy And Large-Scale, Decentralized Networks - Matan Field','','inherit','closed','closed','','186-revision-v1','','','2016-03-21 08:27:56','2016-03-21 08:27:56','',186,'http://magazine.backfeed.cc/186-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(552,1,'2016-03-21 08:30:38','2016-03-21 08:30:38','<p>[embed]https://youtu.be/LPE7Z9Fu5Nc[/embed]</p><p>What would it look like if billions of people would be spontaneously, freely and systematically cooperating with each other, on anything? Imagine a self-organized world, with Facebook network but no Facebook Inc., a decentralized transportation network without Lyft or Uber, peer-to-peer marketplaces replacing eBay or Amazon, millions of people insuring each others and building startups together.</p>','Stigmergic Economy And Large-Scale, Decentralized Networks - Matan Field','','inherit','closed','closed','','186-revision-v1','','','2016-03-21 08:30:38','2016-03-21 08:30:38','',186,'http://magazine.backfeed.cc/186-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(553,1,'2016-03-21 08:31:47','2016-03-21 08:31:47','<p>[emb